    "IntroductionThe image captioning task integrates computer vision and natural language processing to generate descriptive captions for visual inputs.",
    "With the development of Artificial Intelligence, image captioning techniques have been increasingly applied in various fields.",
    "Such as medicine [5,28], fashion and e-commerce [19], aided industry [36], and tourism [4].",
    "Moreover, this technology shows immense potential in traffic applications.",
    "The traditional computer vision task mainly detects and classifies targets such as pedestrians, obstacles, signage, etc."
